    "en": {
      "title": "Schools will resume from today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the traffic problem caused by fuel shortage, the activities of government and government sanctioned private schools, which were given a holiday for the past few weeks, will resume from today.",
        "Also, the first installment of learning activities for the year 2022 has been extended till the 7th of September.",
        "The Ministry of Education has announced that the timing of the second and third semester learning activities will be announced later.",
        "In this regard, the Ministry of Education has issued a statement that teaching activities will be held in schools only on Mondays, Tuesdays and Thursdays. (a)"
      ],
